  "title": "Foundations of The Importance of Play in Learning: Understanding the Role of Play in Cognitive Development",
  "lessonText": "Play is essential for cognitive development in youth.",
  "data": {
    "content": "• Play enhances creativity and imagination.\n• Engaging in play helps develop problem-solving skills.\n• Social interactions during play improve communication abilities.\n• Play fosters emotional regulation and resilience.\n• Learning through play makes education enjoyable and effective."
  }
}
